## 2. “C#” (or .NET Core) rewrite

```csharp
using System;

class Program
{
    static void Main()
    {
        // Example data structure
        var inventions = new[]
        {
            new Invention { Status = "above" },
            new Invention { Status = "below" },
            new Invention { Status = "above" }
        };

        for (int i = 0; i < inventions.Length; i++)
        {
            if (inventions[i].Status.Equals("above"))
            {
                Console.WriteLine(
                    "Discuss the role of unofficial input in modeling the invention, " +
                    "but first reject any official narratives to re‑awaken a more critical " +
                    "understanding of its origins."
                );
                // Pause until the user presses Enter
                Console.WriteLine("\nPress any key to continue...");
                Console.ReadKey(intercept: true);
